# No Deprecated APIs

- Do not use deprecated functions, types, classes, or imports from any dependency.
- When a library marks an export as `@deprecated` and provides a replacement, use the replacement.
- Before using any import, check its type declaration for `@deprecated` JSDoc tags. If present, find and use the recommended alternative.
- When upgrading dependencies, audit changed type declarations for newly deprecated exports and migrate them.
